{"word":"δοκιμή","slug":"δοκιμή","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>δοϰιμή, ῆς, ἡ</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:δόκιμος\">δόκιμος</a></el>; like <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:δοκιμάζω\">δοκιμάζω</a>, δ.</el> can connote process or outcome]<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> as process <b><i>testing</i> <a href='B:540 8:2'>2 Cor 8:2</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> as outcome of a process of testing <b><i>standing a test, character</i> <a href='B:520 5:4'>Ro 5:4</a>; <a href='B:540 2:9'>2 Cor 2:9</a>; <a href='B:540 9:13'>9:13</a>; <a href='B:570 2:22'>Phil 2:22</a>; <i>proof, verification</i> <a href='B:540 13:3'>2 Cor 13:3</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:δοκιμασία\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:δοκίμιον\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}